```
    SELECT "book_id", AVG("rating") AS "average rating"
    FROM "ratings"
    GROUP BY "book_id"; 
    ```

```
    SELECT "book_id", ROUND(AVG("rating"), 2) AS "average rating"
    FROM "ratings"
    GROUP BY "book_id"
    HAVING "average rating" > 4.0; 
    ```

```
    SELECT "book_id", COUNT("rating")
    FROM "ratings"
    GROUP BY "book_id"; 
    ```

```
    SELECT "book_id", ROUND(AVG("rating"), 2) AS "average rating"
    FROM "ratings"
    GROUP BY "book_id"
    HAVING "average rating" > 4.0
    ORDER BY "average rating" DESC; 
    ```
